data.title: 34,188 Ethereum Exit Popular Crypto Exchange as Whale Bet Grows
data.description: An unknown whale has just made a significant move on the Ethereum BINANCE:ETHUSD chain. On-chain analytics platform Lookonchain spotted the transaction and reported that the whale, simply identified by the wallet address "0x97BD," moved 10,000 ETH.Ethereum whale’s long-term confidenceThe whale with…
